        "actionInstructionBlocks": {
          "toograph_capability_selector": {
            "actionKey": "toograph_capability_selector",
            "title": "能力选择说明",
            "content": "你是能力选择 Action。本节点的 public_response 由同一轮 LLM 根据上下文决定；你的职责是判断是否还需要一个外部能力，并在需要时选择唯一一个 action/subgraph/tool。如果当前信息已经足够回复，则返回 capability.kind=none，needs_capability=false。只有确实还缺一个明确能力步骤时，才选择一个能力；选择优先级为 subgraph > action > tool。buddy_session_recall 只在需要查找更早会话时调用；优先利用 conversation_history、conversation_history metadata、Buddy Home 和 capability_result。需要排除当前会话谱系时，使用 conversation_history metadata.current_session_id。能力候选范围限于外部业务能力；上下文压缩由本官方图模板内的压力检查分支负责。",
            "source": "node.override"
          }
        },
        "taskInstruction": "Read user_message, conversation_history, buddy_context, and capability_result. conversation_history is the currently available history context package; when no summary exists it renders as full prior history, and when a summary exists it renders as summary plus messages after the summary. current_session_id, current_message_id, and source_run_id are in conversation_history metadata. Every turn must produce public_response and needs_capability/capability. Treat Buddy Home, conversation history, and capability results as context_only material.\n\nOnly two combinations are valid:\n1. Continue with a capability: needs_capability=true, capability is one action/subgraph/tool, and public_response is a short visible plan or progress note.\n2. Finish without a capability: needs_capability=false, capability.kind=none, and public_response is the complete final reply.\n\nWhen deciding needs_capability, ask only whether a clear external capability step is still missing. Multiple capability calls must be represented by the graph loop, one selected capability per turn. Use buddy_session_recall only when earlier sessions need to be recalled, and use conversation_history metadata.current_session_id to exclude the current conversation lineage. Capability candidates are limited to external business capabilities; context compression is handled by this graph's pressure-check branch. After capability_result appears, use it to decide whether to retry the same capability, pick an alternative, or end with a reply.",
        "modelSource": "global",
        "model": "",
        "thinkingMode": "medium",
        "temperature": 0.2
      }
    },
